{"title_page": "Skr\u0161\u00edn", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Skr\u0161\u00edn\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=Skr\u0161\u00edn - n\u00e1ves 2.JPG\n|image_caption = Center of the village\n|image_shield=\n|image_flag=\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem Region|\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[Most District|Most]]\n|coordinates      = {{coord|50|28|3|N|13|44|55|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n|pushpin_map=Czech Republic| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in the [[Czech Republic]]\n| image_map               = Skrsin MO CZ.png\n| map_caption             = Location in [[Most District]]\n|area_total_km2=6.98\n|population_total=210|population_as_of=2006\n|population_density_km2=auto\n|elevation_m=323\n|postal_code_type=Postal&nbsp;code|postal_code=434&nbsp;01\n|website=http://skrsin.cz\n}}\n\n'''Skr\u0161\u00edn''' ({{lang-de|Skirschina}}) is a village and municipality (''[[obec]]'') in [[Most District]] in the [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem Region]] of the Czech Republic.\n\nThe municipality covers an area of {{convert|6.98|km2|sqmi}}, and has a population of 210 (as at 3&nbsp;July 2006).\n\nSkr\u0161\u00edn lies approximately {{convert|9|km|mi|0}} south-east of [[Most (Most District)|Most]], {{convert|30|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} south-west of [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem]], and {{convert|64|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} north-west of [[Prague]].\n\n== References ==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20100607201619/http://www.czso.cz/lexikon/mos_vdb.nsf/okresy/CZ0425 Czech Statistical Office: Municipalities of Most District]\n\n{{commons category|Skr\u0161\u00edn}}\n{{Most District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Skrsin}}\n[[Category:Villages in Most District]]\n\n\n{{\u00dast\u00ednadLabem-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Skr\u0161\u00edn\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=Skr\u0161\u00edn - n\u00e1ves 2.JPG\n|image_caption = Center of the village\n|image_shield=\n|image_flag=\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem Region|\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[Most District|Most]]\n|coordinates      = {{coord|50|28|3|N|13|44|55|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n|pushpin_map=Czech Republic| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in the [[Czech Republic]]\n| image_map               = Skrsin MO CZ.png\n| map_caption             = Location in [[Most District]]\n|area_total_km2=6.98\n|population_total=210|population_as_of=2006\n|population_density_km2=auto\n|elevation_m=323\n|postal_code_type=Postal&nbsp;code|postal_code=434&nbsp;01\n|website=http://skrsin.cz\n}}\n\n'''Skr\u0161\u00edn''' ({{lang-de|Skirschina}}) is a village and municipality (''[[obec]]'') in [[Most District]] in the [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem Region]] of the Czech Republic.\n\nThe municipality covers an area of {{convert|6.98|km2|sqmi}}, and has a population of 210 (as at 3&nbsp;July 2006).\n\nSkr\u0161\u00edn lies approximately {{convert|9|km|mi|0}} south-east of [[Most (Most District)|Most]], {{convert|30|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} south-west of [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem]], and {{convert|64|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} north-west of [[Prague]].\n\n== References ==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20100607201619/http://www.czso.cz/lexikon/mos_vdb.nsf/okresy/CZ0425 Czech Statistical Office: Municipalities of Most District]\n\n{{commons category|Skr\u0161\u00edn}}\n{{Most District}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Skrsin}}\n[[Category:Villages in Most District]]\n\n\n{{\u00dast\u00ednadLabem-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/