{"title_page": "Skryje (Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District)", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Skryje\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline= Skryje(okres HB) C. NavesDomyZapadniStrana.jpg\n|image_shield=|image_flag=\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[Vyso\u010dina Region|Vyso\u010dina]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District|Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod]]\n|coordinates = {{coord|49|50|36|N|15|29|22|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n|pushpin_map=Czech Republic|area_total_km2= 4.16\n|population_total= 179\n|population_as_of= 1.1.2014\n|population_density_km2= auto\n|elevation_m= 298\n|postal_code_type=Postal&nbsp;code|postal_code=582&nbsp;82\n}}\n\n'''Skryje''' is a village and municipality (''[[obec]]'') in [[Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District]] in the [[Vyso\u010dina Region]] of the Czech Republic.\n\nThe municipality covers an area of {{convert|4.16|km2|sqmi}}, and has a population of 192 (as at 28&nbsp;August 2006).\n\nSkryje lies approximately {{convert|28|km|mi|0}} north of [[Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod]], {{convert|51|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} north of [[Jihlava]], and {{convert|82|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} east of [[Prague]].\n\n==References==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20090512144537/http://czso.cz/lexikon/mos_vdb.nsf/okresy/CZ0611 Czech Statistical Office: Municipalities of Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District]\n\n{{Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Skryje}}\n[[Category:Villages in Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District]]\n\n\n{{Vyso\u010dina-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Skryje\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline= Skryje(okres HB) C. NavesDomyZapadniStrana.jpg\n|image_shield=|image_flag=\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Reg