{"title_page": "Skryje (Brno-Country District)", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Skryje\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=Skryje (okres Brno-venkov) - domy \u010dp. 3 a 21.jpg\n|image_shield=Skryje (okres Brno-venkov) znak.jpg|image_flag=Skryje (okres Brno-venkov) vlajka.jpg\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[South Moravian Region|South Moravian]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[Brno-Country District|Brno-Country]]\n|coordinates = {{coord|49|23|25|N|16|18|36|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n|pushpin_map=Czech Republic|area_total_km2=2.21\n|population_total=55|population_as_of=2006\n|population_density_km2=auto\n|elevation_m=332\n|postal_code_type=Postal&nbsp;code|postal_code=594&nbsp;55\n}}\n\n'''Skryje''' is a village and municipality (''[[obec]]'') in [[Brno-Country District]] in the [[South Moravian Region]] of the Czech Republic.\n\nThe municipality covers an area of {{convert|2.21|km2|sqmi}}, and has a population of 55 (as at 3&nbsp;July 2006).\n\nSkryje lies approximately {{convert|31|km|mi|0}} north-west of [[Brno]] and {{convert|157|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} south-east of [[Prague]].\n\n==References==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20081002192533/http://www.czso.cz/lexikon/mos_vdb.nsf/okresy/CZ0623 Czech Statistical Office: Municipalities of Brno-Country District]\n\n{{commons category|Skryje (Brno-Country District)}}\n{{Brno-Country District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Skryje}}\n[[Category:Villages in Brno-Country District]]\n\n\n{{SouthMoravia-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Skryje\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=Skryje (okres Brno-venkov) - domy \u010dp. 3 a 21.jpg\n|image_shield=Skryje (okres Brno-venkov) znak.jpg|image_flag=Skryje (okres Brno-venkov) vlajka.jpg\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivisio